Class OMStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • agents.anac.y2013.MetaAgent.portfolio.thenegotiatorreloaded.OMStrategy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NullStrategy

    public abstract class OMStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the abstract class which determines when the opponent model may be updated, and how it used to select a bid for the opponent.
